Connection URL: mysql://$OPENSHIFT_MYSQL_DB_HOST:$OPENSHIFT_MYSQL_DB_PORT/

You can manage your new MySQL database by also embedding phpmyadmin-3.4.
The phpmyadmin username and password will be the same as the MySQL credentials above.



You can get a list of cartridges by running

rhc cartridge list
You can manage the cartridge by running one of these commands

rhc cartridge start -a open -c mysql-5.1
rhc cartridge stop -a open -c mysql-5.1
rhc cartridge restart -a open -c mysql-5.1
rhc cartridge reload -a open -c mysql-5.1
rhc cartridge status -a open -c mysql-5.1
